title: ⚖️ Supreme Court sides with Real Madrid in TV rights row with LaLiga
description: The Supreme Court (TS) has dealt a blow to LaLiga by annulling a crucial part of its statutes that regulated the distribution of audiovisual rights for the 2015/2016 season, according to Europa Press....
